Package: thesisdown
Title: An updated R Markdown thesis template using the bookdown package
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Chester", "Ismay", email = "chester.ismay@gmail.com", role = "cre"),
    person("Nick", "Solomon", email = "nick@nicksolomon.me", role = "aut"),
    person("Brittney", "Bailey", email = "bebailey@amherst.edu", role = "aut"))
Description: Using the bookdown package and LaTeX and Word thesis templates from
    Reed College, this package aims to encourage reproducible research using
    simple Markdown syntax while embedding all of the R code to produce plots
    and analyses as well. This package has been modified for use at Amherst College.
Maintainer: Brittney E. Bailey <bebailey@amherst.edu>
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.0),
    devtools,
    dplyr,
    ggplot2,
    bookdown,
    knitr
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
SystemRequirements: pandoc (>= 1.18) - http://pandoc.org
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
